<template>
  Home
</template>

<script>

import {onMounted} from "vue";

export default {
  name: "Home",
  props: ['mqttClient'],
  setup(){

    onMounted(()=>{
      this.mqttClient
          .then((client) => {
            client.on('connect', ()=> {
              console.log("client: " + client)
            })
          })
          .catch((err) => {
            console.log(err)
          });
      })
  }
}
</script>

<style scoped>

</style>
